4^{2n+1}+3^{n+2}
13x = 4^{2n+3}+3^{n+3}
13x = 16*4^{2n+1}+3*3^{n+2}
\frac{13}{3}x = \frac{16}{3}*4^{2n+1}+3^{n+3}
\frac{13}{3}x = \frac{13}{3}*4^{2n+1}+4^{2n+1}+3^{n+3}
13m
\frac{13}{3}x = \frac{13}{3}*4^{2n+1}+13m
x = 4^{2n+1}+3m
 \frac{4^{2n+3} + 3^{n+3}}{13} = \frac{13 \cdot 4^{2n+1} + 3\left(4^{2n+1} + 3^{n+1} \right)}{13} = \frac{13\cdot 4^{2n+1} + 3 \cdot 13m}{13} \in \mathbb{Z} 
